Bali Nine ringleaders Andrew Chan and Myruan Sukumaran will be led from their isolated cells to a place called Nirbaya - or Death Valley - in the depths of the jungle .
The men will be given white clothing to wear, which symbolises the afterlife, before facing the firing squad at the stoke of midnight on Tuesday night .
They will also be given a choice whether to stand, sit or kneel before a cross is placed over their hearts acting as a target for the shooting squad .
